# This directory contains Terraform modules for the unified DevOps Agent Workshop
# Modules:
# - vpc/           - Shared VPC for both ECS and EKS
# - ecs/           - ECS cluster and services
# - eks/           - EKS cluster and addons
# - dependencies/  - Shared backends (RDS, DynamoDB, ElastiCache, MQ)
# - security-groups/ - Shared security groups
